text: Sweden competed at the 1984 Winter Paralympics in Innsbruck, Austria. They won seven gold medals, two silver medals and five bronze medals and finished 6th in the medal table. == See also == * Sweden at the Paralympics * Sweden at the 1984 Winter Olympics == References == Category:Sweden at the Paralympics Category:1984 in Swedish sport Category:Nations at the 1984 Winter Paralympics
title: Sweden at the 1984 Winter Paralympics
